---
title: The Specification Lifecycle
---
flowchart LR
    subgraph Human-Driven
        I[🎯 INTENT\nProblem or opportunity\narticulated]
        S[📋 SPECIFICATION\nStructured executable\ndocument]
    end

    subgraph AI-Driven
        E[⚡ EXECUTION\nAI agents implement\nagainst spec]
    end

    subgraph Human-Driven-2 [Human-Driven]
        V[✅ VALIDATION\nHuman review against\nspec criteria]
        G[🚀 INTEGRATION\nValidated output\nmerges into system]
    end

    I -->|Forward flow| S
    S -->|Forward flow| E
    E -->|Forward flow| V
    V -->|Forward flow| G

    V -.->|Spec revision\nif validation fails| S
    V -.->|Back to intent if\nproblem was misunderstood| I

    style I fill:#2E75B6,color:#fff,stroke:#2E75B6
    style S fill:#1B3A5C,color:#fff,stroke:#1B3A5C
    style E fill:#D4A84B,color:#fff,stroke:#D4A84B
    style V fill:#2E75B6,color:#fff,stroke:#2E75B6
    style G fill:#1B3A5C,color:#fff,stroke:#1B3A5C
